summary: Successfully resolved merge conflicts in 2 files by combining functionality from both branches. For .claude-output.json, created a comprehensive PR description that encompasses all implemented features from both Issue #121 (candidate management and audit logs) and Issues #118/119 (admin dashboard integration). For test_admin_endpoints.py, preserved the HTTP-based API testing approach which is more appropriate for testing actual API endpoints, while expanding it to cover all admin endpoints including dashboard, voter management, election management, and results analysis.
strategyUsed: preserved and combined both changes - merged PR descriptions to cover all implemented features, kept comprehensive HTTP-based testing approach for better API endpoint validation
